  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "SCi Games published a Game Boy Color title of Thunderbirds in 2000.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "Join the Tracy Family in seven old-school mini-games across various locations in the world in order to thwart the evil Hood. The game allows players to control Thunderbirds vehicles 1-4, The mole and FAB1 in a variety of mini-games:* TB1, a recon and combat craft, is a side scrolling mini-game involving bombing and shooting ground and air targets while looking for people to rescue and collecting intel on the area.",
